      <h3 id="title">Easygard Mobile Amtgard</h3>
      <p>This web application is a subset of the Amtgard V8 rulebook (rules) optimized for viewing on mobile devices. Comments and suggestions are welcome.</p>
      <p>This application is <b>No Longer offline capable</b>! The browsers removed the app cache functionality that was used. Investigating other options.</p>
      <p>The content of this application is provided by the <a href="https://www.amtgard.com/documents">Amtgard V8 rules of play documents</a> and the implementation of the mobile application is done by <a href="mailto:kismet@felfrost.ca?Subject=Easygard.ca Inquiry" target="_top">Lord Kismet of Felfrost</a> with help from <a href="https://ork.amtgard.com/orkui/?Route=Player/index/171316">The Wizard of Hats</a>.  There is no intent to derive monetary value from this application and the source can be found at the <a href="https://github.com/kenwalker/easygard.ca">Github repository for Easygard.ca</a>.</p>
      <p>Amtgard Playtest Guide V8.6.4 "Sappy Four". Please contact me if something is missing or looks incorrect</p>
      <h3>Bugs/Suggestions</h3>
      <p>Please report any bugs or suggestions to the <a href="mailto:kismet@felfrost.ca?Subject=Easygard.ca bug" target="_top">kismet@felfrost.ca</a> email address</p>
      <p>You may be interested in some of my other Amtgard apps and utilities:
