        <li><a href="https://kenwalker.github.io/jsork/index.html">jsork</a> - JavaScript Amtgard ORK APIs and numerous reports</li>
        <li><a href="https://m.facebook.com/amtquest/">AmtQuest Chest</a> - A physical box with much tech trying to travel the lands of Amtgard</li>
      </ul>
